videos.description: Kenrich Williams finds Alex Robinson who finishes with the nice scoop layup between defenders for TCU.
videos.headline: TCU's Robinson with the scoop layup between defenders

videos.description: Tacko Fall with the block that leads to a 3-pointer for UCF's Nick Banyard.
videos.headline: Defense leads to offense for UCF

videos.description: UCF's coach Johnny Dawkins talks about the difference of having Tacko Fall on and off the floor.

videos.description: Alex Robinson with the great lob to Kenrich William who finishes with the powerful alley-oop for TCU.
